Package request

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EventRequest
    Information for event method Domain: authToken : unique auth token eventID : the event's unique ID
    EventsRequest
    Information for event(all) method Domain: authToken : unique auth token
    FillRequest
    Informations for fill method Domain: userName : Non-empty String generations : Optional int value
    LoadRequest
    The “users” property in the request body contains an array of users to be created.
    LoginRequest
    Contains information needed to log in the user Domain: userName : Non-empty string password : Non-empty string
    PeopleRequest
    Information for person(all) method Domain: authToken : unique auth token
    PersonRequest
    Information for person method Domain: authToken : unique auth token personID : Person's unique ID
    RegisterRequest
    An object that contains all the information necessary to register when register method is called Domain: userName : Non-empty String password : Non-empty String email : Non-empty String firstName : Non-empty String lastName : Non-empty String gender : "f" or "m"
